{"tha-ap381:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap381:0.2":"Bodhivandanavagga ","tha-ap381:0.3":"Sumanadamiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap381:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap381:1.2":"nhatakassa tapassino; ","tha-ap381:1.3":"Katvana sumanadamam, ","tha-ap381:1.4":"dharayim purato thito. ","tha-ap381:2.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap381:2.2":"yam damam dharayim tada; ","tha-ap381:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap381:2.4":"sumanadharane phalam. ","tha-ap381:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap381:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap381:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap381:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap381:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap381:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap381:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap381:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap381:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap381:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sumanadamiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap381:7.1":"Sumanadamiyattherassapadanam navamam. "}